trans-unit.source: A static extension methods class for getting a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message> instance from an <xref href="System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: En statisk utvidelsen metoder klasse for å få en <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message>serverforekomsten fra en <xref href="System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage"> </xref> forekomsten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message>

trans-unit.source: Creates a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message> instance from an <xref href="System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage"></xref> instance.
The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message> instance can be read, written and copied just as a traditional <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ByteStreamMessage> instance.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message>forekomsten kan leses, skrives og kopiert bare som en tradisjonell <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ByteStreamMessage>forekomsten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ByteStreamMessage> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message> instance can also "read" to retrieve the original <xref:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage> instance by calling the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageExtensionMethods.ToHttpResponseMessage%2A> extension method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message>forekomsten kan også "lese" for å hente opprinnelig <xref:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage>forekomsten ved å kalle den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageExtensionMethods.ToHttpResponseMessage%2A>utvidelsen-metoden.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.MessageExtensionMethods.ToHttpResponseMessage%2A> </xref:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage"></xref> from which to create the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.Message> instance.
